            Email: lei.yang@uci.edu





Research Interests:


Optimization algorithm design for high-performance and low-power computing in Network-on-Chip based Multiprocessor System-on-Chips, communication efficiency and temperature optimization for thermo-reliable many-core systems, and multi-core architecture
design and high-performance parallel computing in Non-volatile Memory (NVM) based NoCs.

